<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.882984>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Dorsal habitus of Euconnus (Diarthroconnus) birnbacheri Ganglbauer, female lectotype (Austria) (1) and Euconnus (s. str.) fimetarius (Chaudoir), female (Poland) (2)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/882984/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.882988>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 7. Morphological structures of Euconnus (Diarthroconnus) birnbacheri Ganglbauer, female lectotype (5 – 6) and original set of labels of lectotype (7). Left antenna in dorsal view (5); pterothorax in ventral view (6). Abbreviations: pcr, procoxal rest; msvp, mesoventral intercoxal process; mtvp, metaventral intercoxal process." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/882988/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

